---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SectionDivider from '../components/SectionDivider.astro';
import Icon from '../components/Icon.astro';

---

<Layout 
  title="The Council | The Parlour — The World's Most Exclusive Society of Magic"
  description="Meet The Council — the distinguished leaders who guide The Parlour, the world's most exclusive private magic society. Stewards of tradition and excellence."
  keywords="magic, exclusive magic club, private magic society, magic council, magic leadership"
  ogUrl="https://theparlour.com/the-council"
  ogImage="https://theparlour.com/image/hero-board.jpg"
>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section content-hero content-hero-board">
        <div class="content-container">
            <h1>The Council</h1>
            <p class="lead">The guardians of our tradition</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Introduction Section -->
    <section class="content-info">
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>Our Leadership</h2>
            <div class="content-row">
                <div class="content-col content-col-full">
                    <div class="content-details-card">
                        <h3>Stewards of the Art</h3>
                        <p>The Council is the governing body of The Parlour, entrusted with safeguarding the society's vision, legacy, and standards of excellence. Composed of distinguished members who have demonstrated unwavering dedication to the craft, each Council member upholds the traditions that define our institution.</p>
                        <p>Together, they curate the experiences, set the standards, and ensure that The Parlour remains the world's most prestigious sanctuary for the magical arts.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Council Mystery Section -->
    <section class="content-info">
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>The Shrouded Council</h2>
            <div class="content-row">
                <div class="content-col content-col-full">
                    <div class="content-details-card">
                        <h3>Identities Unknown. Authority Absolute.</h3>
                        <p>The current members of The Council are shrouded in absolute secrecy. Their identities are known only to one another and to the most senior members of the society. This is by design — and by tradition stretching back centuries.</p>
                        <p>Legend holds that the original Council was formed in an age when practitioners of the arcane arts faced persecution and suspicion. To protect both the art and its guardians, the founders decreed that those who lead shall do so from the shadows. The Council governs not through visibility, but through wisdom, discretion, and an unwavering commitment to the preservation of magic's deepest secrets.</p>
                        <p>What is known: The Council convenes in private. Their decisions shape every aspect of The Parlour — from who is granted admission to which ancient techniques are passed to the next generation. They are the keepers of the flame, ensuring that the art endures in its purest form.</p>
                        <p><em>Those who seek to know The Council must first prove themselves worthy of the society itself. Only then, in time, may the veil be lifted.</em></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Board Responsibilities Section -->
    <section class="location-details">
        <div class="content-container">
            <div class="content-row">
                <div class="content-col content-col-full">
                    <h2>Council Responsibilities</h2>
                    <div class="content-row">
                        <div class="content-col">
                            <div class="expectation-item">
                                <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="clipboard" /></span>
                                <div>
                                    <h4>Society Governance</h4>
                                    <p>The Council oversees all facets of The Parlour's operations, from strategic direction and financial stewardship to upholding the standards that define our institution. They ensure the society remains true to its mission of preserving and advancing the magical arts.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="content-col content-col-half content-mt-medium">
                            <div class="expectation-item">
                                <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="masks" /></span>
                                <div>
                                    <h4>Curated Experiences</h4>
                                    <p>From exclusive gatherings and masterclasses to private performances, The Council curates every event with meticulous attention. They secure world-class guest artists, orchestrate competitions, and create unparalleled opportunities for members to refine their craft.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="content-col content-col-half content-mt-medium">
                            <div class="expectation-item">
                                <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="chain" /></span>
                                <div>
                                    <h4>Member Cultivation</h4>
                                    <p>The Council nurtures the growth of every member, pairing emerging practitioners with seasoned mentors and fostering an environment where knowledge is exchanged with generosity and discretion.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="content-col content-mt-medium">
                            <div class="expectation-item">
                                <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="globe" /></span>
                                <div>
                                    <h4>Community Presence</h4>
                                    <p>Representing The Parlour in the broader world, The Council cultivates relationships with distinguished magical organizations, coordinates select public engagements, and elevates the art of magic throughout San Diego.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="content-col content-mt-medium">
                            <div class="expectation-item">
                                <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="speech" /></span>
                                <div>
                                    <h4>Contribute</h4>
                                    <p>Members in good standing are welcome to attend Council sessions and offer their perspective — a privilege we hold in high regard. Formal votes are reserved for Council members. We encourage those with vision to seek a seat at the table.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Succession Section -->
    <section class="what-to-expect">
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>The Rite of Succession</h2>
            <div class="content-row">
                <div class="content-col content-col-two-thirds content-offset-col">
                    <div class="expectation-list">
                        <div class="expectation-item">
                            <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="ballot" /></span>
                            <div>
                                <h4>The Selection</h4>
                                <p>When the time comes for the Council to evolve, a sacred selection process is set into motion. Only a rare few are considered — those whose mastery of the craft, depth of character, and devotion to the society have been observed and quietly noted over the course of their membership. The selection is never rushed. It unfolds with the deliberation that has governed this society since its founding.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="expectation-item">
                            <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="people" /></span>
                            <div>
                                <h4>The Nomination</h4>
                                <p>Candidates for the Council are put forward through a confidential nomination process, known only to those within the inner circle. A nomination is not a campaign — it is a recognition. Those who are named have already proven themselves through years of silent dedication, and their candidacy is weighed with the gravity it deserves.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="expectation-item">
                            <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="scale" /></span>
                            <div>
                                <h4>Term of Service</h4>
                                <p>The duration of a Council member's service is determined within the Council itself, guided by a confluence of factors: the length and distinction of one's tenure, demonstrated mastery of the magical arts, financial stewardship of the society's legacy, and an enduring commitment to the values upon which The Parlour was built. Some serve for a season. Others, for a lifetime. The Council alone decides.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action Section -->
    <section class="attending-info">
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>The Path Begins Here</h2>
            <div class="content-row content-align-center">
                <div class="content-col content-col-full">
                    <div class="attendance-info" style="text-align: center; max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;">
                        <p>The Council is not a position one applies for — it is a distinction one earns through years of unwavering service to The Parlour and the art itself. But every journey toward the Council begins the same way: by first becoming a member of the society.</p>
                        <p>If you believe you possess the dedication, the skill, and the character to walk among the world's most distinguished practitioners of magic, your path starts with a single step.</p>
                        <p class="content-mt-medium cta-mobile-center"><a href="#" class="content-btn open-contact-form">Request an Invitation</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
   
    <SectionDivider type="wave" />
</Layout>
